acle of Bacon</a> - Based on an <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Six_Degrees_of_Kevin_Bacon\">online game</a> that resulted in a <a href=\"http://www.sixdegrees.org/\">charity</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-03-31T01:32:38.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"briatte/awesome-network-analysis","categoryHTML":"<h2>Varia</h2><h3>Small Worlds</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.cornell.edu/video/six-degrees-of-separation-panel\">Panel: Six Degrees of Separation</a> - Video of a conference at Cornell University, featuring Duncan J. Watts, Steven H. Strogatz, Jon Kleinberg and other speakers.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-03-31T01:32:38.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"briatte/awesome-network-analysis","categoryHTML":"<h2>Varia</h2><h3>Small Worlds</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://badhessian.org/2013/09/patterns-in-the-ivy-the-small-world-of-metal/\">Patterns in the Ivy: The Small World of Metal</a> - Example of a two-mode network analysis based on metal artists and bands.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-03-31T01:32:38.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"briatte/awesome-network-analysis","categoryHTML":"<h2>Varia</h2><h3>Small Worlds</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://sixdegreesoffrancisbacon.com/\">Six Degrees of Francis Bacon</a> - Interactive visualization of a well-documented early modern historical network.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-03-31T01:32:38.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"briatte/awesome-network-analysis","categoryHTML":"<h2>Varia</h2><h3>Small Worlds</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Six_degrees_of_separation\">Six Degrees of Separation</a> - Wikipedia English entry.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-03-31T01:32:38.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"vinta/awesome-python","categoryHTML":"<h2>URL Manipulation</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/gruns/furl\">furl</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/gruns/furl\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span sty